# =============================================================================
# Environment Variables for Agent Workflows Web App
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to .env and update with your actual values

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# REQUIRED - Server will not start without these
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# JWT Secret - Used to sign and verify authentication tokens
# IMPORTANT: Use a strong, random secret in production
# Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
JWT_SECRET=your-secret-key-change-in-production

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTIONAL - Server will use defaults if not specified
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Logging level - Options: trace, debug, info, warn, error, fatal
# Default: info
LOG_LEVEL=info

# Log file path - Where to write log files
# Logs are written to both console and this file in all environments:
# - Development: Pretty-formatted console + JSON file
# - Production: JSON stdout + JSON file
# Default: ./logs/app.log
LOG_FILE=./logs/app.log

# CORS - Comma-separated list of allowed origins for cross-origin requests
# Default: http://localhost:5173
# Production example: https://yourdomain.com,https://www.yourdomain.com
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173

# Server Configuration
# Default: 3456
PORT=3456

# Default: 127.0.0.1
HOST=127.0.0.1

# Vite Development Server
# Default: 5173
VITE_PORT=5173

# Node Environment
NODE_ENV=development

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# AI Model API Keys - For session name generation and AI features
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Anthropic API Key - Used to generate session names from chat conversations
# Get your key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-api-key

# Server Configuration
PORT=3456
HOST=127.0.0.1

# Vite Development Server
VITE_PORT=5173

# JWT Authentication
JWT_SECRET=change-this-to-a-secure-random-string-in-production

# Node Environment
NODE_ENV=development
